		<td><b>Re: RDF profile field</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><strong>Done</strong><br /><br />I made an &quot;RDF URL&quot; field that can be used for an RSS feed of your website or for your FOAF profile. I tested it by putting a link to the Atom feed of my wiki's Recent Changes page. I originally hesitated because each new profile field is something that moderators have to police for unwarranted self-promotion or other unconstructive behavior.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
